Technological Stack:

This application should be hosted in one of the cloud deployments like AWS Beanstalk or Azure.
This should be a .Net application stack with similar base as NerdDinner.
The application should have a data structure such as a graph to show adjacent available car drivers on a map in a 5 mile radius
This application should allow for drivers and riders to come online or go offline instantaneously. 
This application should show information such as the car make and model or picture and contact info between the interested parties.


